Package model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a User that creates an account. The user is serializable and has a username and a password. The user also has a list of albums associated with it. There is also a constructor in this class for a stock user that has stock for its username and password.
    Author:
    Brian Schillaci
